    <section_number>15</section_number>
    <catch_line>Superintendent And Deputies; Residences</catch_line>
    <order_by>15</order_by>
    <text>
        The superintendent, and his deputy, shall reside constantly within the precincts of the correctional institution, unless otherwise authorized by the commissioner.
    </text>
